#find no. of lines, word count, byte and characters count

* wc file (Count no. of char)

* wc file1 file2 (more than 1 file)

* wc -l file (total lines)

* wc -l file1 file2 (same)

* wc -w file (total words)

* wc -m file (total characters) 

* wc -c file (total bytes)

* wc -L file (show longest line)